content: Today's AI is jack of all trades master of none. If we need a specialist AI, we need to train it to be that. And this trained AI will be all proprietory, private. So, AI trainer and fine tuners will be in demand.
I have taken MBT test and it suggests I am a logician(?) INTP-T... Will take another test a few months from now... Lets see if it changes
